longBusinessSummary: Diligent Media Corporation Limited engages in the distribution of news through digital media in India. It also operates a news website, www.dnaindia.com. The company offers content through DNA Syndication. Diligent Media Corporation Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Noida, India.
